he "many faced diamond" analogy for god at the end of http://groups.yahoo.c=
om/group/vedic-wisdom/message/1 to get clarity on why different people give=
 different hierarchies and consider different beings as supreme. As per Nar=
ayana sooktam, all gods (including Brahma, Vishnu, Shiva, Indra etc) came f=
