duality is the underlying supreme reality in duality. Thus, the hierarchy w=
ithin hierarchy will have to start at the connection with non-duality and i=
t is not one. In other words, any hierarchy given by anyone is with respect=
 to one perspective. I will not be too keen on finalizing one hierarchy, be=
