rst?
 
There is no causal relationship between the two. Actions of rishis a=
nd the will of the supreme cosmic being are in sync. They just happen toget=
her. Neither causes the other.
 
Rishis are the most perfected beings witho=
ut a trace of ego and yet performing actions of great consequence, with zer=
o attachment. They operate right on the border of duality and non-duality.
