man who may be the highest authority. But, it may be a ceremonial role and =
some may consider CEO to be higher while some may consider the chairman to =
be higher. Why bother about who is higher? In a company does well, they bot=
h work with understanding.
 
The hierarchy is irrelevant to one who is a cl=
erk at the company. Just follow the order of your boss (guru) instead of wo=
ndering whether chairman calls the shots or CEO.
 
